  "original_title": "\u0d86\u0dba\u0dd4\u0db0\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9f \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca 15 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sergeant arrested with weapon remanded until 15",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Additional Magistrate Keminda Perera ordered today 11 to remand the Mechanical Police Sergeant of the Police Transport Division who was arrested by the Fort Police while standing in front of the Presidential Secretariat wearing a police uniform and carrying a sharp weapon.",
        "A police mechanical sergeant attached to the Police Transport Division residing at First Lane, Samagi Mawatha, Magammana, Homagama was remanded in custody.",
        "The Fort Police informed the court that this suspect police officer was arrested near the main entrance of the office today (11) at 4:10 am while he was standing near the Presidential Secretariat office with a knife in his hand which could be used to commit a crime."
      ],
